content:
GTA+ Members can claim the Heartbreakers Jacket and Heartbreakers Cap (Forwards or Backwards) and the Lunar New Year Shirt and Pants, available in both Black and Red.

GTA+ Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
